{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GRimV7H9uckv4Aq31yh5uW","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→@use \"palette\" as *;\n     2→\n     3→// ============================================================\n     4→// Bar toggle button\n     5→// ============================================================\n     6→\n     7→.notif-toggle-wrap {\n     8→  position: relative;\n     9→}\n    10→\n    11→// Flat-top hexagon badge (Chrysaki status indicator shape)\n    12→.notif-badge {\n    13→  clip-path: polygon(25% 0%, 75% 0%, 100% 50%, 75% 100%, 25% 100%, 0% 50%);\n    14→  background: $error;\n    15→  color: $text-primary;\n    16→  font-size: 9px;\n    17→  font-weight: bold;\n    18→  min-width: 16px;\n    19→  min-height: 16px;\n    20→  padding: 0px 2px;\n    21→}\n    22→\n    23→// ============================================================\n    24→// Panel window (glassmorphism — compositor blur provides depth)\n    25→// ============================================================\n    26→\n    27→.notif-panel {\n    28→  background-color: rgba(15, 17, 23, 0.15);\n    29→  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n    30→  box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n    31→  padding: 10px;\n    32→  min-width: 320px;\n    33→  max-width: 400px;\n    34→}\n    35→\n    36→// --- Panel header ---\n    37→\n    38→.notif-panel-header {\n    39→  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n    40→  padding-bottom: 6px;\n    41→  margin-bottom: 4px;\n    42→}\n    43→\n    44→.notif-panel-title {\n    45→  color: $text-primary;\n    46→  font-size: 15px;\n    47→  font-weight: bold;\n    48→  padding: 4px 0px;\n    49→}\n    50→\n    51→.notif-clear-all-btn {\n    52→  background: transparent;\n    53→  border: none;\n    54→  color: $text-muted;\n    55→  font-size: 11px;\n    56→  padding: 2px 6px;\n    57→  min-width: 0px;\n    58→\n    59→  &:hover {\n    60→    color: $error;\n    61→  }\n    62→}\n    63→\n    64→.notif-dnd-btn {\n    65→  background: transparent;\n    66→  border: none;\n    67→  color: $text-secondary;\n    68→  font-size: 16px;\n    69→  padding: 2px 4px;\n    70→  min-width: 0px;\n    71→\n    72→  &:hover {\n    73→    color: $text-primary;\n    74→  }\n    75→}\n    76→\n    77→.notif-dnd-active {\n    78→  color: $blonde-light;\n    79→}\n    80→\n    81→// ============================================================\n    82→// Panel notification list\n    83→// ============================================================\n    84→\n    85→.notif-panel-list {\n    86→  padding: 4px 0px;\n    87→}\n    88→\n    89→.notif-empty {\n    90→  color: $text-muted;\n    91→  font-size: 12px;\n    92→  padding: 16px 0px;\n    93→}\n    94→\n    95→// ============================================================\n    96→// Notification row (chamfered Chrysaki container)\n    97→// clip-path produces the 8px chamfer; borders are omitted as\n    98→// clip-path clips them off — use background tint instead.\n    99→// ============================================================\n   100→\n   101→.notif-row {\n   102→  clip-path: polygon(\n   103→    8px 0%,\n   104→    calc(100% - 8px) 0%,\n   105→    100% 8px,\n   106→    100% calc(100% - 8px),\n   107→    calc(100% - 8px) 100%,\n   108→    8px 100%,\n   109→    0% calc(100% - 8px),\n   110→    0% 8px\n   111→  );\n   112→  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);\n   113→  padding: 8px 12px;\n   114→\n   115→  &:hover {\n   116→    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);\n   117→  }\n   118→}\n   119→\n   120→// Urgency modifier: critical notifications get Error red tint\n   121→.notif-row-critical {\n   122→  background: rgba(140, 47, 57, 0.15);\n   123→\n   124→  &:hover {\n   125→    background: rgba(140, 47, 57, 0.25);\n   126→  }\n   127→\n   128→  .notif-row-app {\n   129→    color: $blonde-light;\n   130→  }\n   131→}\n   132→\n   133→.notif-row-header {\n   134→  margin-bottom: 2px;\n   135→}\n   136→\n   137→.notif-row-app {\n   138→  color: $teal-light;\n   139→  font-size: 11px;\n   140→  font-weight: bold;\n   141→}\n   142→\n   143→.notif-row-time {\n   144→  color: $text-muted;\n   145→  font-size: 10px;\n   146→}\n   147→\n   148→.notif-dismiss-btn {\n   149→  background: transparent;\n   150→  border: none;\n   151→  color: $text-muted;\n   152→  font-size: 12px;\n   153→  padding: 0px 2px;\n   154→  min-width: 0px;\n   155→\n   156→  &:hover {\n   157→    color: $error;\n   158→  }\n   159→}\n   160→\n   161→.notif-row-summary {\n   162→  color: $text-primary;\n   163→  font-size: 13px;\n   164→  font-weight: bold;\n   165→}\n   166→\n   167→.notif-row-body {\n   168→  color: $text-secondary;\n   169→  font-size: 12px;\n   170→  margin-top: 2px;\n   171→}\n   172→\n   173→// ============================================================\n   174→// Notification action buttons\n   175→// ============================================================\n   176→\n   177→.notif-actions {\n   178→  margin-top: 6px;\n   179→  padding-top: 4px;\n   180→  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);\n   181→}\n   182→\n   183→.notif-action-btn {\n   184→  background: rgba(26, 138, 106, 0.15);\n   185→  border: 1px solid rgba(26, 138, 106, 0.3);\n   186→  color: $emerald-light;\n   187→  font-size: 11px;\n   188→  padding: 3px 8px;\n   189→  min-width: 0px;\n   190→\n   191→  &:hover {\n   192→    background: rgba(26, 138, 106, 0.3);\n   193→    border-color: $emerald-light;\n   194→    color: $text-primary;\n   195→  }\n   196→\n   197→  &:active {\n   198→    background: rgba(26, 138, 106, 0.45);\n   199→  }\n   200→}\n   201→\n   202→// ============================================================\n   203→// Toast popup window (layer-shell, TOP | RIGHT anchor)\n   204→// High alpha background: toasts float without compositor blur.\n   205→// ============================================================\n   206→\n   207→.notif-toast-list {\n   208→  padding: 0px;\n   209→}\n   210→\n   211→// Chamfered toast card — matches .notif-row shape at larger scale\n   212→.notif-toast {\n   213→  clip-path: polygon(\n   214→    8px 0%,\n   215→    calc(100% - 8px) 0%,\n   216→    100% 8px,\n   217→    100% calc(100% - 8px),\n   218→    calc(100% - 8px) 100%,\n   219→    8px 100%,\n   220→    0% calc(100% - 8px),\n   221→    0% 8px\n   222→  );\n   223→  background: rgba(28, 31, 43, 0.92); // $surface at high alpha\n   224→  padding: 10px 14px;\n   225→  min-width: 300px;\n   226→  max-width: 380px;\n   227→\n   228→  &:hover {\n   229→    background: rgba(37, 40, 54, 0.95); // $raised at high alpha\n   230→  }\n   231→}\n   232→\n   233→// Urgency modifier: critical toasts get Error red background\n   234→.notif-toast-critical {\n   235→  background: rgba(140, 47, 57, 0.88);\n   236→\n   237→  &:hover {\n   238→    background: rgba(181, 63, 74, 0.92);\n   239→  }\n   240→\n   241→  .notif-toast-app {\n   242→    color: $blonde-light;\n   243→  }\n   244→}\n   245→\n   246→.notif-toast-header {\n   247→  margin-bottom: 3px;\n   248→}\n   249→\n   250→.notif-toast-app {\n   251→  color: $emerald-light;\n   252→  font-size: 11px;\n   253→  font-weight: bold;\n   254→}\n   255→\n   256→.notif-toast-close {\n   257→  background: transparent;\n   258→  border: none;\n   259→  color: $text-muted;\n   260→  font-size: 12px;\n   261→  padding: 0px 2px;\n   262→  min-width: 0px;\n   263→\n   264→  &:hover {\n   265→    color: $error;\n   266→  }\n   267→}\n   268→\n   269→.notif-toast-summary {\n   270→  color: $text-primary;\n   271→  font-size: 13px;\n   272→  font-weight: bold;\n   273→}\n   274→\n   275→.notif-toast-body {\n   276→  color: $text-secondary;\n   277→  font-size: 12px;\n   278→  margin-top: 2px;\n   279→}\n   280→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6df22c68-10e5-4fe6-b063-9fbbcc257cca","uuid":"ec8169ea-eaee-4c15-86b7-7621a5559518","timestamp":"2026-03-17T11:30:09.332Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/home/kiriketsuki/dots/chrysaki-ralph-ags-notification-center/ags/.config/ags/styles/_notifications.scss","content":"@use \"palette\" as *;\n\n// ============================================================\n// Bar toggle button\n// ============================================================\n\n.notif-toggle-wrap {\n  position: relative;\n}\n\n// Flat-top hexagon badge (Chrysaki status indicator shape)\n.notif-badge {\n  clip-path: polygon(25% 0%, 75% 0%, 100% 50%, 75% 100%, 25% 100%, 0% 50%);\n  background: $error;\n  color: $text-primary;\n  font-size: 9px;\n  font-weight: bold;\n  min-width: 16px;\n  min-height: 16px;\n  padding: 0px 2px;\n}\n\n// ============================================================\n// Panel window (glassmorphism — compositor blur provides depth)\n// ============================================================\n\n.notif-panel {\n  background-color: rgba(15, 17, 23, 0.15);\n  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n  box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n  padding: 10px;\n  min-width: 320px;\n  max-width: 400px;\n}\n\n// --- Panel header ---\n\n.notif-panel-header {\n  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n  padding-bottom: 6px;\n  margin-bottom: 4px;\n}\n\n.notif-panel-title {\n  color: $text-primary;\n  font-size: 15px;\n  font-weight: bold;\n  padding: 4px 0px;\n}\n\n.notif-clear-all-btn {\n  background: transparent;\n  border: none;\n  color: $text-muted;\n  font-size: 11px;\n  padding: 2px 6px;\n  min-width: 0px;\n\n  &:hover {\n    color: $error;\n  }\n}\n\n.notif-dnd-btn {\n  background: transparent;\n  border: none;\n  color: $text-secondary;\n  font-size: 16px;\n  padding: 2px 4px;\n  min-width: 0px;\n\n  &:hover {\n    color: $text-primary;\n  }\n}\n\n.notif-dnd-active {\n  color: $blonde-light;\n}\n\n// ============================================================\n// Panel notification list\n// ============================================================\n\n.notif-panel-list {\n  padding: 4px 0px;\n}\n\n.notif-empty {\n  color: $text-muted;\n  font-size: 12px;\n  padding: 16px 0px;\n}\n\n// ============================================================\n// Notification row (chamfered Chrysaki container)\n// clip-path produces the 8px chamfer; borders are omitted as\n// clip-path clips them off — use background tint instead.\n// ============================================================\n\n.notif-row {\n  clip-path: polygon(\n    8px 0%,\n    calc(100% - 8px) 0%,\n    100% 8px,\n    100% calc(100% - 8px),\n    calc(100% - 8px) 100%,\n    8px 100%,\n    0% calc(100% - 8px),\n    0% 8px\n  );\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);\n  padding: 8px 12px;\n\n  &:hover {\n    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);\n  }\n}\n\n// Urgency modifier: critical notifications get Error red tint\n.notif-row-critical {\n  background: rgba(140, 47, 57, 0.15);\n\n  &:hover {\n    background: rgba(140, 47, 57, 0.25);\n  }\n\n  .notif-row-app {\n    color: $blonde-light;\n  }\n}\n\n.notif-row-header {\n  margin-bottom: 2px;\n}\n\n.notif-row-app {\n  color: $teal-light;\n  font-size: 11px;\n  font-weight: bold;\n}\n\n.notif-row-time {\n  color: $text-muted;\n  font-size: 10px;\n}\n\n.notif-dismiss-btn {\n  background: transparent;\n  border: none;\n  color: $text-muted;\n  font-size: 12px;\n  padding: 0px 2px;\n  min-width: 0px;\n\n  &:hover {\n    color: $error;\n  }\n}\n\n.notif-row-summary {\n  color: $text-primary;\n  font-size: 13px;\n  font-weight: bold;\n}\n\n.notif-row-body {\n  color: $text-secondary;\n  font-size: 12px;\n  margin-top: 2px;\n}\n\n// ============================================================\n// Notification action buttons\n// ============================================================\n\n.notif-actions {\n  margin-top: 6px;\n  padding-top: 4px;\n  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);\n}\n\n.notif-action-btn {\n  background: rgba(26, 138, 106, 0.15);\n  border: 1px solid rgba(26, 138, 106, 0.3);\n  color: $emerald-light;\n  font-size: 11px;\n  padding: 3px 8px;\n  min-width: 0px;\n\n  &:hover {\n    background: rgba(26, 138, 106, 0.3);\n    border-color: $emerald-light;\n    color: $text-primary;\n  }\n\n  &:active {\n    background: rgba(26, 138, 106, 0.45);\n  }\n}\n\n// ============================================================\n// Toast popup window (layer-shell, TOP | RIGHT anchor)\n// High alpha background: toasts float without compositor blur.\n// ============================================================\n\n.notif-toast-list {\n  padding: 0px;\n}\n\n// Chamfered toast card — matches .notif-row shape at larger scale\n.notif-toast {\n  clip-path: polygon(\n    8px 0%,\n    calc(100% - 8px) 0%,\n    100% 8px,\n    100% calc(100% - 8px),\n    calc(100% - 8px) 100%,\n    8px 100%,\n    0% calc(100% - 8px),\n    0% 8px\n  );\n  background: rgba(28, 31, 43, 0.92); // $surface at high alpha\n  padding: 10px 14px;\n  min-width: 300px;\n  max-width: 380px;\n\n  &:hover {\n    background: rgba(37, 40, 54, 0.95); // $raised at high alpha\n  }\n}\n\n// Urgency modifier: critical toasts get Error red background\n.notif-toast-critical {\n  background: rgba(140, 47, 57, 0.88);\n\n  &:hover {\n    background: rgba(181, 63, 74, 0.92);\n  }\n\n  .notif-toast-app {\n    color: $blonde-light;\n  }\n}\n\n.notif-toast-header {\n  margin-bottom: 3px;\n}\n\n.notif-toast-app {\n  color: $emerald-light;\n  font-size: 11px;\n  font-weight: bold;\n}\n\n.notif-toast-close {\n  background: transparent;\n  border: none;\n  color: $text-muted;\n  font-size: 12px;\n  padding: 0px 2px;\n  min-width: 0px;\n\n  &:hover {\n    color: $error;\n  }\n}\n\n.notif-toast-summary {\n  color: $text-primary;\n  font-size: 13px;\n  font-weight: bold;\n}\n\n.notif-toast-body {\n  color: $text-secondary;\n  font-size: 12px;\n  margin-top: 2px;\n}\n","numLines":280,"startLine":1,"totalLines":280}}}
