X_VISIBLE=4, FIFO queue, GLib.timeout_add 5000ms auto-dismiss, DND-aware enqueue (skip toast if notifd.dontDisturb), ToastRow (app/summary/body labels + close button), notif-toast-critical class on urgency CRITICAL, notifd connect \"notified\" and \"resolved\" signals, export NotificationToast(). | T11 |"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
